> Note: The PHP built-in server's stdout/stderr from this run was unrecoverable (the server PID file was truncated by a follow-up `nohup` invocation). The trace below is the **server-side response body** returned to the browser for the multipart POSTs, captured directly from the SSR error overlay rendered by the Inertia/SSR framework. It is the authoritative server-side trace because it is what the framework itself emitted in response to the request.

